      "id": "PopularPost196770",
      "post_content": "\"One of the most ridiculously overrated cards I've ever seen. This card sees literally zero competitive play in constructed formats (except maybe in Block? I don't play Block), and isn't even that interesting in casual play.\"  \n- Henrietta  \n  \nSo you don't play block... do you actually believe that means the ratings of those who do are irrelevant?  \n  \nTake a look, 3 of the 8 top decks here used Flame Slash:  \nhttp://www.wizards.com/Magic/Magazine/Article.aspx?x=mtg/daily/eventcoverage/ptsj10/t8blockdecklists  \n  \nAs for casual, your comment shows a decided lack of imagination. As of this writing, an advanced Gatherer search shows 64 different creatures with toughness 4 and a rating of 4.5 or above; to kill such a creature for ![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol) is a bargain.  \n  \nWith the thousands of MtG cards that have been printed over the years, surely you can come up with an \"interesting\" deck concept that utilizes Flame Slash.",
      "posted_by": "helluin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost196770\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">\"One of the most ridiculously overrated cards I've ever seen. This card sees literally zero competitive play in constructed formats (except maybe in Block? I don't play Block), and isn't even that interesting in casual play.\"<br/>- Henrietta<br/><br/>So you don't play block... do you actually believe that means the ratings of those who do are irrelevant?<br/><br/>Take a look, 3 of the 8 top decks here used Flame Slash:<br/>http://www.wizards.com/Magic/Magazine/Article.aspx?x=mtg/daily/eventcoverage/ptsj10/t8blockdecklists<br/><br/>As for casual, your comment shows a decided lack of imagination.  As of this writing, an advanced Gatherer search shows 64 different creatures with toughness 4 and a rating of 4.5 or above; to kill such a creature for <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=R&amp;type=symbol\"/> is a bargain.<br/><br/>With the thousands of MtG cards that have been printed over the years, surely you can come up with an \"interesting\" deck concept that utilizes Flame Slash.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy53665\">helluin</span>\r\n            