      "id": "PopularPost241956",
      "post_content": "Reasons to hold your [Lightning Bolt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt)s until your turn anyway:  \n  \n[Wee Dragonauts](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wee Dragonauts)  \n[Charmbreaker Devils](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Charmbreaker Devils)  \n[Gelectrode](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gelectrode)  \n[Kiln Fiend](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Kiln Fiend)  \n  \nAll of these creatures will allow you to get extra (better) mileage out of your instants if you cast them on your turn. Might as well swap your Lightning Bolts for Flame Slash with these creatures and use it to clear your path.  \n  \nJust depends on the other cards in your deck.",
      "posted_by": "alphagprime",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost241956\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Reasons to hold your <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt\">Lightning Bolt</a>s until your turn anyway:<br/><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wee Dragonauts\">Wee Dragonauts</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Charmbreaker Devils\">Charmbreaker Devils</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gelectrode\">Gelectrode</a><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Kiln Fiend\">Kiln Fiend</a><br/><br/>All of these creatures will allow you to get extra (better) mileage out of your instants if you cast them on your turn. Might as well swap your Lightning Bolts for Flame Slash with these creatures and use it to clear your path.<br/><br/>Just depends on the other cards in your deck.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy78921\">alphagprime</span>\r\n                                (4/30/2012 11:01:17 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n             